Class SwerveDrive2018

  • java.lang.Object
    • Subsystem
      • org.usfirst.frc.team5002.drive.swerve.SwerveDrive2018
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drive, SwerveDrive

    public class SwerveDrive2018
extends Subsystem
implements SwerveDrive
    This class manages all four swerve modules and does calculations for wheel angle, wheel speed, etc. This class also implements SwerveDrive.
